": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, he has returned to South Korea with glory and joy after the historic event.\", \"from\": 6991, \"to\": 7071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7015, \"end\": 7026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.822312204823989e-23, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 16, fans flocked to the Incheon International Airport to welcome Jin back home after his monumental global achievement.\", \"from\": 7073, \"to\": 7200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7105, \"end\": 7134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Incheon International Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 7146, \"end\": 7149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7988825721946793e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a casual denim fit, the K-pop star exuded radiance as he greeted the fans with open arms.\", \"from\": 7201, \"to\": 7293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, the site was crowded with ARMYs and other netizens who wanted to get a glimpse of this global superstar who kicked off the Paris Olympics torch relay.\", \"from\": 7295, \"to\": 7452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 14, BTS' Jin participated in the torch relay for the Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 7466, \"to\": 7541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7478, \"e