\"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, he has completed the filming for the MBC variety show The Half-Star Hotel in Lost Island.\", \"from\": 8428, \"to\": 8530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His episodes will soon be broadcast.\", \"from\": 8531, \"to\": 8567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand,Jinhas confirmed that he is working on his solo album, which he plans to release soon.\", \"from\": 8569, \"to\": 8673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He revealed that he has received over 4,000 song submissions from producers for this album.\", \"from\": 8674, \"to\": 8765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reports suggest the BTS member's first solo album will arrive in the late second half of this year.\", \"from\": 8767, \"to\": 8866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8787, \"end\": 8790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5621823123139328e-80, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:BTS' Jin says he received 4000 to 5000 song submissions after confirming upcoming solo album plans\", \"from\": 8868, \"to\": 8976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8878, \"end\": 8881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5621823123139328e-80, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}, {\"begin\": 8883, \"end\": 8886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7988825721946793e-13, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"h